{"title":"(Vue) 元件型別驗證","uid":"ee5f16e22cae164521223be8474bac52","slug":"元件型別驗證","date":"2021-08-12T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.896Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/元件型別驗證.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"型別技巧\"><a href=\"#型別技巧\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"型別技巧\"></a>型別技巧</h2><p>以下用三種方式，來查看結果：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>使用 input 標籤來綁定輸入數值：會呈現字串</li>\n<li>直接賦予數值上去：會呈現字串</li>\n<li>使用 v-bind 綁定數值：才會呈現原始的資料型別</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;h3&gt;Props 型別技巧&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;\n&lt;input type&#x3D;&quot;number&quot; v-model&#x3D;&quot;money&quot;&gt;\n\n&lt;props-type money&#x3D;&quot;300&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;props-type&gt;\n&lt;props-type :money&#x3D;&quot;money&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;props-type&gt;\n&lt;props-type :money&#x3D;&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;props-type&gt;\n&lt;props-type :money&#x3D;&quot;&#123;&#125;&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;props-type&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-jsx\" data-language=\"jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">  const app &#x3D; Vue.createApp(&#123;\n    data() &#123;\n      return &#123;\n        money: 300,\n      &#125;;\n    &#125;,\n  &#125;);\n\n  app.component(&#39;props-type&#39;, &#123;\n    props: [&#39;money&#39;],\n    template: &#96;&lt;div&gt;value: &#123;&#123;money&#125;&#125;, typeof:&#123;&#123; typeof money &#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&#96;\n  &#125;);\n\napp.mount(&#39;#app&#39;);</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"定義-Props-型別驗證\"><a href=\"#定義-Props-型別驗證\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定義 Props 型別驗證\"></a>定義 Props 型別驗證</h2><p>如果一次需要使用多種型別驗證技巧，必須使用 object 來做包裹內容，</p>\n<p>常用的範例：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>型別驗證</li>\n<li>預設值、是否必填</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Demo:</p>\n<iframe height=\"300\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"Vue 3 Props 驗證型別\" src=\"https://codepen.io/michael-luo/embed/RwVzqjr?default-tab=html%2Cresult&theme-id=dark\" frameborder=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\">\n  See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/michael-luo/pen/RwVzqjr\">\n  Vue 3 Props 驗證型別</a> by Michael Luo (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/michael-luo\">@michael-luo</a>)\n  on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>\n","text":"型別技巧以下用三種方式，來查看結果： 使用 input 標籤來綁定輸入數值：會呈現字串 直接賦予數值上去：會呈現字串 使用 v-bind 綁定數值：才會呈現原始的資料型別 &lt;h3&gt;Props 型別技巧&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt; &lt;input type&#x...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/categories/Vue.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9E%8B%E5%88%A5%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">型別技巧</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E7%BE%A9-Props-%E5%9E%8B%E5%88%A5%E9%A9%97%E8%AD%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">定義 Props 型別驗證</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"(Vue) Props 向內層元件傳遞資料狀態","uid":"246e2d523d5abb09b5ea4ba84af8f20e","slug":"Props-向內層元件傳遞資料狀態","date":"2021-08-13T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.191Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Props-向內層元件傳遞資料狀態.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"靜態資源傳入圖片連結範例： 在建立好的 app.component 方法內建立 props 變數且帶入一個陣列 array，且新增資料 url 將 template 帶上 &lt;img&gt; 標籤，且使用 v-bind:src=&quot;url&quot; 在 html 內...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/categories/Vue.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":21,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}]